snippet.title: The Wind's Path Trailer
snippet.description:
The Top Down Platformer is available for Steam Next Fest!
Play the demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3114920/The_Winds_Path_Demo/

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2424500/The_Winds_Path/

The Wind's Path is a top-down #platformer #indiegame I'm making with the #godotengine

#gameplay running on the #SteamDeck
